            .anchor#design
            .container
                .columns
                    .column.is-3
                        %p.eyebrow Design
                        %h3 Design System & Style guide
                    .column.is-8.is-offset-1
                        =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/if-web-colors.png", :loading => 'lazy'
        .case-studies__navigation-wrapper.if-web
                        =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/style-guide-if.png", :loading => 'lazy'
        .case-studies__navigation-wrapper.if-web
        .case-study__hifi-wireframes
            .anchor#highfi
            .hifi-wireframes__main-visual
                .container
                    %p.eyebrow High-fi Wireframes
                    %h3 Introducing Island Finance
                    %p A personal loan experience designed to feel simple, clear, and trustworthy. From the first screen to the final step, every detail was crafted to guide users smoothly and make financial decisions less intimidating.
                    .btn__wrapper
                        = link_to "View Wireframes", "https://xd.adobe.com/view/1e1ff4df-ea06-42fb-9f58-5e2db1da0c82-4b4c/", :class => "btn", :target => "blank"
                    .img__wrapper
                        = video_tag("https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Island-Finance-Home.mp4", :autobuffer => "true", :autoplay => "true", :loop => "true", :muted => "true", :controls => "true", :playsinline => "true" )
            .hifi-wireframes__loan-options
                .container
                    %h4 Simplifying the Loan Decision Journey
                    %p To make the decision-making process feel easy and transparent and help users feel supported, we designed this page to balance education, reassurance, and action. It starts by answering the first thing most users want to know: “Is this loan actually a good fit for me?” with a quick breakdown of the key benefits.
                    %p From there, we added customer reviews to build trust. A simple “what you'll need” checklist sets expectations early, reducing stress or potential abandonment later in the flow. The 3-step overview keeps the process approachable, and the FAQs address common concerns upfront so users don't have to hunt for answers.
                    .columns
                        .column.is-4
                            .img__wrapper
                                =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Loan+Options.jpg", :loading => 'lazy'
        .case-studies__navigation-wrapper.if-web
                        .column.is-8
                            .img__wrapper
                                = video_tag("https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Island-Finance-Personal-Loans.mp4", :autobuffer => "true", :autoplay => "true", :loop => "true", :muted => "true", :controls => "true", :playsinline => "true" )
            .hifi-wireframes__loan-calculator.is-hidden-touch
                .columns.is-variable.is-gapless
                    .column.is-2-fullhd.is-3-widescreen
                        .loan-calculator__text-wrapper
                            %h4
                                Designing a Win–Win
                                %br
                                Loan Calculator Experience
                            %p We designed a loan calculator that lets users explore estimated payments without affecting their credit, paired with a transparent breakdown of rates and fees. After checking their rate, users can create an account to save their progress and later manage their loan online. From a business side, collecting contact details at this stage helps nurture potential applicants and improve conversions.
                    .column.is-5
                        .img__wrapper
                            =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/IF-Calculator.png", :loading => 'lazy'
                    .column.is-5-fullhd.is-4-widescreen
                        .img__wrapper
                            =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Island+Finance+Sign+Up.png", :class => "hifi__signup-img", :loading => 'lazy'
            .hifi-wireframes__loan-calculator.is-hidden-desktop
                .columns.is-variable.is-multiline
                    .column.is-12
                        .loan-calculator__text-wrapper
                            %h4
                                Designing a Win–Win
                                %br
                                Loan Calculator Experience
                            %p We designed a loan calculator that lets users explore estimated payments without affecting their credit, paired with a transparent breakdown of rates and fees. After checking their rate, users can create an account to save their progress and later manage their loan online. From a business side, collecting contact details at this stage helps nurture potential applicants and improve conversions.
                    .column.is-6
                        .img__wrapper
                            =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/IF-Calculator.png", :loading => 'lazy'
                    .column.is-6
                        .img__wrapper
                            =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Island+Finance+Sign+Up.png", :class => "hifi__signup-img", :loading => 'lazy'
            .hifi-wireframes__loan-application
                .container
                    .loan-application__text-wrapper
                        %h4 Making Applications Feel Easy
                        %p Form fatigue is common in financial applications, so we focused on making a step-by-step loan application that helps users see their progress and stay engaged. At the end, transparent fees and flexible loan options help users choose what best fits their needs and budget.
                    .columns.is-multiline
                        .column.is-8
                            .img__wrapper
                                =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Island+Finance+Loan+Information.png", :loading => 'lazy'
                        .column.is-4.is-hidden-mobile
                            .img__wrapper
                                =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Loan+Application.jpg", :loading => 'lazy'

            .hifi-wireframes__account.short
                .container
                    .columns.masonry
                        .column.is-6
                            .columns.is-multiline
                                .column.is-12
                                    .account__text-wrapper
                                        %h4 Helping Users Stay in Control After Approval
                                        %p To help users avoid feeling lost after their loan is approved and improve self-service, we designed a dashboard that gives them full visibility and control over their account. Users can easily track payments, review documents, manage autopay, and adjust settings, all in one space. This helps prevent missed payments and builds confidence in managing their finances.
                                .column.is-12
                                    .img__wrapper
                                        =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Island+Finance+Dashboard.png", :loading => 'lazy'
                                .column.is-12
                                    .img__wrapper
                                        =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Island+Finance+Payment.png", :loading => 'lazy'
                        .column.is-6
                            .img__wrapper
                                =image_tag "https://nicolada-website.s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com/Island+Finance+Settings.png", :loading => 'lazy'
